uid: jdoe
cn: John Doe
sn: Doe
mail: jdoe@example.com
employeeNumber: 123456
ðŸ”’ Notes:
Use LDAPS (SSL) in production.

You can change USER_FILTER to something like:

python
Copy
Edit
USER_FILTER = '(&(objectClass=inetOrgPerson)(uid=jdoe))'
If Directory Manager access is not allowed over LDAP, use a service account with appropriate rights.
